<br>
When you get good droppable items that nobody needs, have a guild designated banker sell the items for platinum profit, and put the money in the guildbank.  use that money to buy raid supplies.<br>
<br>
It's wierd how Everquest works.  individuals and guilds are either on the &quot;poor as hell and can't buy a stack of dots&quot; line or the &quot;so rich we could not run out of raid supplies if we purposefully tried&quot; side of the line.<br>
<br>
Wait...thats not really wierd...its kinda like real life.<br>
<br>
So anyway...<br>
<br>
No taxes in most guilds.  Most guilds have a guild leader, and a few officers that sometimes double as raid leaders/recruiters. <p><P><br>
